      "instructions": "Preheat oven to 325.\r\n     Coat a teflon bunt pan with cooking spray and sprinkle with a mixture of cinnamon and sugar mixture.  Combine all ingredients until well mixed; pour batter into prepared pan.  Bake for 55 minutes until cake tester comes out clean.  (Or 35-40 minutes for mini-bundt pans.)  Cool 15 minutes before removing from pan.",
