      "ingredients": "2 garlic cloves\r\n2 15 oz. cans black beans, drained, rinsed\r\n1 small can chopped green chiles, drained\r\n1 Tbs. lemon juice\r\nJuice of 1 lime\r\n1 Tbs. balsamic vinegar\r\n1 tsp. cumin\r\n1/2 tsp. chili powder\r\nDash salt\r\nDash pepper\r\n2 Tbs. cilantro",
