      "name": "Chinese Cabbage Salad",
      "ingredients": "4 C shredded cabbage\r\n1 pkg. Top Raman\r\n4 green onions, sliced (about 1/4 C)\r\n1/2 C slivered almonds, toasted\r\n3 Tbs. rice wine vinegar\r\n2 Tbs. vegetable oil\r\n2 Tbs. sugar\r\n1/2 tsp. white pepper\r\n1/4 tsp. salt\r\n2 Tbs. sesame seeds",
