      "instructions": "In 6-quart heavy pot, over medium heat, brown sausage, stirring to beak up meat.  Stir in peppers and garlic; cook and stir for 2 minutes.  Add stock and diced tomatoes.  Heat to a boil.  Reduce heat; simmer 15 minutes.  Add pasta and cook 10 minutes or until done.  Serve warm sprinkled with cheese.",
