      "ingredients": "FILLING\r\n2 C fresh or frozen cranberries\r\n1/2 C sugar\r\n1/2 C walnuts, chopped\r\n\r\nTOPPING\r\n2 eggs\r\n3/4 C butter, softened\r\n1 C sugar\r\n1 C flour\r\n1 tsp. almond extract",
