      "ingredients": "3 Tbs. orange juice\r\n2 Tbs. low-sodium soy sauce\r\n1 Tbs. rice vinegar\r\n1 Tbs. honey\r\n1 tsp. bottled minced garlic\r\n2 tsp. bottled ground fresh ginger\r\n4 6-ounce salmon fillets (about 1 inch thick)",
