      "ingredients": "2 Tbs. flour\r\n1/2 tsp. salt\r\n1/2 tsp. pepper\r\n1 lb. boneless, skinless chicken breast, cut into 1-inch pieces\r\n2 tsp. canola oil\r\n1 ripe pear, peeled, cored and chopped\r\n3 scallions, sliced\r\n3/4 C apple cider\r\n1/4 C dried cranberries\r\n2 tsp. coarse grain mustard",
