      "id": 658,
      "name": "Vegetable Beef Soup (CP)",
      "ingredients": "1 lb. ground turkey or beef\r\n1 onion, chopped\r\n2 jars (28oz.) spicy pasta sauce\r\n1 can (10.5oz.) beef consume\r\n2 C water\r\n2 cans (14.5oz.) diced tomatoes\r\n1 package (16oz.) frozen mixed vegetables, thawed\r\n1/2 tsp. pepper",
