      "ingredients": "2-1/4 C confectioners' sugar\r\n1/4 tsp. salt\r\n1 tsp. espresso powder, optional but good\r\n1 C cocoa powder\r\n3 large egg whites\r\n2 tsp. vanilla\r\n1 C chocolate chips\r\n1 C chopped nuts",
