      "id": 706,
      "name": "Chocolate-Marshmallow Fondue (CP)",
      "ingredients": "7oz. milk chocolate\r\n3oz. white chocolate\r\n1 C marshmallow fluff\r\n1/4 C evaporated skim milk\r\n1 tsp. almond extract",
