      "ingredients": "1 C dried cranberries\r\n1/2 C coarsely chopped walnuts\r\n1/3 C packed brown sugar\r\n1/2 C water\r\n1 tsp. ground cinnamon \r\n3 Gala Apples, cored and chopped (about 1.5 pounds)",
