      "id": 813,
      "name": "Horseradish Salmon Burgers",
      "ingredients": "1 lb. skinless salmon filet, cut up\r\n2 scallions, sliced\r\n2 eggs\r\n1/3 to 1/2 C bread crumbs\r\n3 Tbs. prepared horseradish\r\n3/4 tsp. kosher salt\r\n1/4 tsp. black pepper\r\n2 Tbs. olive oil",
      "instructions": "In food processor, pulse all ingredients, except for olive oil, until coarsely chopped; form into 4 patties.  Cook in 2 tablespoons olive oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium until opaque throughout, 6 to 7 minutes per side.  Serve with soft buns, mayonnaise and lettuce.",
