      "ingredients": "Â¾ C water\r\nÂ¾ C milk\r\n3 Tbs. butter, cut into pieces\r\n3 C bread flour\r\n1 C whole wheat flour\r\n3 Tbs. light or dark brown sugar\r\n1 Tbs. plus 2 tsp. sesame seeds\r\n1 Tbs. plus 2 tsp. gluten\r\n2 tsp. salt\r\n2-3/4 tsp. bread machine yeast",
