      "ingredients": "1-1/4 lb. ground turkey\r\n1 packet ranch-style dressing mix\r\n2 medium shallots, minced\r\n12 Tbs. Buffalo Wing Sauce, divided\r\n1 Tbs. minced garlic\r\n5 hamburger bun\r\n10 Tbs. fat-free ranch dressing, or light Blue Cheese dressing for garnish",
