      "ingredients": "1-3/4 C uncooked penne pasta\r\n1 lb. ground beef or turkey\r\n1 tsp. minced garlic\r\n1 can (15oz.) tomato puree\r\n1 can (14-1/2oz.) beef broth\r\n1-1/2 tsp. Italian seasoning\r\n1 tsp. Worcestershire sauce\r\n1/4 tsp. salt\r\n1/4 tsp. pepper\r\n2-4 C fresh baby spinach\r\nFresh shredded Parmesan",
