      "ingredients": "3/4 C butter, softened\r\n1 C sugar\r\n1 egg\r\n1-3/4 C flour\r\n1/2 C baking cocoa\r\n1/4 tsp. salt\r\n1/4 tsp. baking soda\r\n3 oz. white baking chocolate, chopped\r\n2 tsp. canola oil, divided\r\n3 oz. semisweet chocolate, chopped\r\n1/4 C crushed candy canes (about 10 miniature)",
