      "ingredients": "1 can (21oz.) cherry or apple pie filling\r\n1 pkg. (regular size) yellow cake mix\r\n1/2 C unsalted butter, melted\r\n1/3 C chopped walnuts, optional",
      "instructions": "Place pie filling in a 1-1/2-quart slow cooker.  Combine the cake mix and butter (the mixture will be crumbly); sprinkle over filling.  Sprinkle with walnuts if desired.  Cover and cook on low for 2-3 hours.  Serve in bowls.",
