      "name": "Honey Mustard Baked Salmon",
      "ingredients": "1-1/2 to 2 lbs. salmon fillets\r\n3 Tbs. honey mustard (1-1/2 Tbs. honey plus 1-1/2 Tbs. Dijon mustard)\r\n3 cloves garlic, minced\r\n3 Tbs. olive oil\r\n1 Tbs. lemon juice\r\n1 Tbs. chopped fresh dill\r\nPinch of salt",
